{"tid":780823,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"散咗仲會唔會同ex聯絡？","createTime":"2018-08-15T12:26:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-15T14:41:42.000Z","uid":78074,"like":11,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"d12b3d6ae55269a8b4203a11c325a500f35c693e","tid":780823,"uid":78074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T12:26:33.000Z","msg":"之前散咗<br />\n佢間唔中都會text下我吹水<br />\n都係問兩句最近番學番工點果啲<br />\n<br />\n但有時唔係好想覆佢<br />\n因為佢條仔非常唔鍾意佢搵我<br />\n將心比己如果自己條女撩個ex傾偈<br />\n我都可能會嬲到想打撚死人<br />\n所以我都從來唔主動搵佢<br />\n<br />\n我都有認真同佢講過<br />\n大概話咪搵我啦費事瓜田李下<br />\n佢又好堅決話唔好<br />\n同埋我都唔想少個朋友<br />\n因為我識左佢好耐<br />\n就算散咗都可以傾到兩句<br />\n<br />\n大家點睇"},{"pid":"214779b39556079ffbcffac25e023d881817078e","tid":780823,"uid":51250,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T12:28:17.000Z","msg":"睇人㗎啫"},{"pid":"4eeea8c138d095ca8de408ecbde282e00a215c60","tid":780823,"uid":142855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T12:32:50.000Z","msg":"唔好啦<br />\n我係佢條仔想打柒你之外，<br />\n對條女都唔會認真<br />\n<br />\n我都可以搵下啲ex<br />\n睇下邊個做得出位啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8ec0e2764c8a445a1f3e30600a6c34b022a85f8","tid":780823,"uid":81575,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T12:36:29.000Z","msg":"唔好累人啦"},{"pid":"9c30962cbea0fddeef7fd039fb54debfd890fdce","tid":780823,"uid":78074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4eeea8c138d095ca8de408ecbde282e00a215c60","tid":780823,"uid":142855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T12:32:50.000Z","msg":"唔好啦<br />\n我係佢條仔想打柒你之外，<br />\n對條女都唔會認真<br />\n<br />\n我都可以搵下啲ex<br />\n睇下邊個做得出位啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T12:40:28.000Z","msg":"條仔係好仔黎既<br />\n我知咁樣對佢唔公平<br />\n就算唔係帽佢都影響到人<br />\n所以你啱 唔好再搵佢了"},{"pid":"a91b278778337935a4bb7f0ace3027634384a4da","tid":780823,"uid":129506,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-0