e":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T13:11:54.000Z","msg":"同呢種人keep contact要識say no<br />\n絕啲"},{"pid":"cf7b567ea546801a3572e857768476e1dba26bd2","tid":780823,"uid":49859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T13:13:56.000Z","msg":"睇下邊個飛邊個"},{"pid":"5a5c344be88e3412238bfa33f81fc02688a33b93","tid":780823,"uid":98507,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T13:22:31.000Z","msg":"現時仲有聯絡得返3個EX都仲聯絡緊 其中一個結埋婚<br />\n其實好多都傾得返 好似得2個EX係冇聯絡過<br />\n傾返之後發現左唔少以前冇發覺到嘅事<br />\n例如拍拖嗰陣自己有D固執 偏見 或者一直都唔了解佢<br />\n又會FF如果冇左呢D問題到底會點呢<br />\n不過諗深一層 可能就係因為太著緊同顧慮到對方感情<br />\n所以好多野都冇講出口 寧願收收埋埋 造成誤會<br />\n而且做朋友唔怕麻煩到對方呀嘛<br />\n倒不如話正因為係朋友所以有麻煩先會敢講同搵佢幫手<br />\n對住情人好難講 怕對方會厭棄<br />\n<br />\n有時亦都覺得...<br />\n好彩分左手 果然冇做錯決定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16afc2d5962608f9e58913713510173b29de7422","tid":780823,"uid":119307,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T13:30:27.000Z","msg":"散左年半仲有聯絡 係我搵佢但佢冇應過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1073cd222ddf10b92a993ba8b9af3de0b089330c","tid":780823,"uid":27416,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T13:33:37.000Z","msg":"試探下可唔可以做sp<br />\n無就斬纜了"},{"pid":"843b14f35248dbea034abcf1afd69001d4a27a07","tid":780823,"uid":155818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T13:34:27.000Z","msg":"傾親都嘈交<br />\n無謂"},{"pid":"7bf7e04a22afd36a42b9d3487361dfdc23265a65","tid":780823,"uid":186432,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"16afc2d5962608f9e58913713510173b29de7422","tid":780823,"uid":119307,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T13:30:27.000Z","msg":"散左年半仲有聯絡 係我搵佢但佢冇應過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T13:35:01.000Z","msg":"咁樣算咩連絡<br />\n唔好搞尻人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98d26fdb3196169